<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1912-03-05T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1912-03-05T00:00:00-05:00" n="565" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d565">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 033.1100K77/81.]</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">American Minister</gloss> to
                                the <gloss type="to">Acting Secretary of State</gloss></hi>.</head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Santo Domingo</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1912-03-05">
                                    <hi rend="italic">March 5, 1912</hi></date>.</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>I have just been officially advised that the Dominican Minister at
                            Washington has informed the Government of the official note of the
                            Department announcing the proposed visit of Mr. Knox. The Minister for
                            Foreign Affairs said to me: “This pleasing news has been received by my
                            Government with real satisfaction, and I can assure your excellency that
                            such an illustrious visitor will receive the warmest of welcome in
                            Dominican territory.”</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Russell.</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>